    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avius</ex></expan> Ianuarius <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> vivus fecit <lb n="2"/>condita sepulcro hic pausat Ursa <lb n="3"/>C<expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>restiana</abbr></expan> <note>sic</note> fidelis <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XXXVIII per partum <lb n="4"/>subito ducente inpio fato est tradita Tartaris <lb n="5"/>imis et me subito linquit sibi coniugem pro tempo<lb break="no" n="6"/>re iunctum quem <note>sic</note> ambulo et qu<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>ero</abbr></expan> miser quem <note>sic</note> ipse <lb n="7"/>aeterna condidi terra o quit <note>sic</note> tribuat genesis <lb n="8"/>qui <note>sic</note> separat convirginios dulcis <note>sic</note> ut non licuit <lb n="9"/>nobis iugiter supernam frunisci caritatem <lb n="10"/>hoc dico legentibus et lacrimis prosequor verba <lb n="11"/>coniuncti amantis <note>sic</note> semper se bene dicere debent <lb n="12"/>quia nihil erit dulcius quam prima iuventus
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>In zwei Teile gebrochen. Material: weiß-grün geäderter Marmor.</p>
            </div>
